sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant LoadBalancer
    participant NodeA
    participant NodeB
    participant MonitoringSystem

    User->>LoadBalancer: Request Service
    LoadBalancer->>NodeA: Forward Request
    NodeA-->>LoadBalancer: Response
    LoadBalancer-->>User: Deliver Response

    Note over NodeA, MonitoringSystem: NodeA fails
    MonitoringSystem->>LoadBalancer: Alert NodeA Failure
    LoadBalancer->>NodeB: Forward Request
    NodeB-->>LoadBalancer: Response
    LoadBalancer-->>User: Deliver Response

    Note over User: Minimal impact during failover